query:
SELECT id, mealType, calories, beverageType, beverageVolumeMl, DATE_FORMAT(loggedAt, '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i:%s') as loggedAt_formatted
FROM meals 
WHERE clientId = 1 
AND DATE(loggedAt) = '2026-01-22'
ORDER BY loggedAt DESC;
